               <app loc="1"><lem> Ὦ</lem><rdg resp="b0157"/>  <rdg resp="b0157">μ[άρτυς (?)</rdg></app> 
               <app loc="2"> <rdg resp="b0157">...]εον</rdg>  <rdg resp="b0157">προσκυνοῦμεν</rdg></app>
